 <item> <title>U.S. Secretary of Education Betsy DeVos Addresses Full Staff</title>
 <link>https://www.ed.gov/news/press-releases/us-secretary-education-betsy-devos-addresses-full-staff</link>
 <description> U.S. Secretary of Education Betsy DeVos began her first day in office by thanking and praising the Department&#039;s career employees for ensuring a smooth and professional transition. DeVos addressed the staff at the Department&#039;s headquarters in Washington, D.C. Prior to her remarks, DeVos began the morning by visiting staff located at the Union Center Plaza and Potomac Center Plaza buildings, and continued meeting with staff one-on-one upon concluding her remarks.</description>
